    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演安娜，与伙伴们一起行动，种下作物、点击收集资源、放置不同道具，在奇妙且不可思议的梦境中轻松玩耍。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【故事概要】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如同往常的平静夜晚，银盘高挂，月光轻柔地照看着所有人入睡。 随着音乐盒的旋律，安娜做了一个梦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那个地方，上下皆是天空。破碎的石块与遗迹在七彩光芒中迷失，交错漂浮。而他们脚下的漂浮云顶仿若大地一般，延伸开来，承载着无限奇思妙想。 为了找到散落在梦境中的伙伴们，安娜与乌拉将种子种下，并通过作物获得的力量，深入梦境的深处去寻找……</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【游戏特色】</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特色鲜明的角色与他们之间的小故事！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259970/extras/7a333db20e89d00a822c7cca06d8ae3c.poster.avif?t=1740621867\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259970/extras/7a333db20e89d00a822c7cca06d8ae3c.webm?t=1740621867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简单的种植与轻松放置！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >种下种子，等待作物成长，通过点击获取灵力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259970/extras/2c45f2c1020b2f45148e94fe82a3211d.poster.avif?t=1740621867\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259970/extras/2c45f2c1020b2f45148e94fe82a3211d.webm?t=1740621867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁并布置各种道具！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集并放置独特的物品，自动收获和采集资源，加快灵力获取速度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259970/extras/a1504630a3f18704f1197d04eedf31c8.poster.avif?t=1740621867\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259970/extras/a1504630a3f18704f1197d04eedf31c8.webm?t=1740621867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开拓探索，逐步解锁插画故事中角色们的可爱互动！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259970/extras/eafa64eff2b2760ca52431767949875f.poster.avif?t=1740621867\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259970/extras/eafa64eff2b2760ca52431767949875f.webm?t=1740621867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259970/extras/eafa64eff2b2760ca52431767949875f.mp4?t=1740621867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>此试玩版内容包含：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3 种不同作物</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>5 种功能各异的特殊道具</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>5 位登场角色之间的互动故事</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>包含开头故事，共计 9 张故事插图</strong></p></li></ul>",
